---
// Process.astro
---

<section id="process" class="pt-32 pb-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="mb-32">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
                <span class="font-label text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] mb-4 block">Methodology v4.0</span>
                <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]">
                    The Architectural <br/><span class="text-primary">Protocol</span>
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 pb-4">
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-light leading-relaxed">
                    A systematic transformation of abstract intelligence into high-performance digital architecture. No templates. Only precision logic.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Atmospheric Visual -->
        <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/15">
            <img alt="Abstract neural network rendering" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50" data-alt="Abstract complex 3D wireframe mesh nodes" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCFudJuUOF910So31NTlQUgBZGjtiLlXCSNC3_MBc0cgMLNktNxgosLELLG8rLmAvDkYnPB4sYBB0VySlLrmxPI3BqDI3hRTo-byboH98X00Aiglp4rNXkfPnNC27mpD1qyrQ1jw3MgxraxOYMk2m7UwtBny2EdUUXhvDRziTcpoi1yP-0l4eWX4gOPOFdmInwofvGYpTUTXetS-edXWHkpq5v-mT0ovsG8cLJXDiTJVSEsAFBzPHOawn4eJRIBaAJ_oavnFgq5M5-W"/>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-12 left-12">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-secondary">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">schema</span>
                    <span class="font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">System Status: Active</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Process Timeline (Asymmetric Layout) -->
    <div class="space-y-48 relative">
        <!-- Central Vertical Guide (Ghost Border) -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-outline-variant/10 hidden lg:block transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>
        
        <!-- Step 01 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 pr-0 lg:pr-24 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(204,151,255,0.05)] relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-primary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-black text-outline-variant/10 absolute -top-4 -right-4">01</span>
                    <span class="font-label text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-6 block">Phase 01: Analysis</span>
                    <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Neural Analysis (Architect + Analysis Agent)</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        We initiate the protocol with deep-dive analysis. The Lead Architect sets the vision, while the Analysis Agent extracts goals, user behavior patterns, and market anomalies from massive data sets.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full text-[9px] font-label uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface-variant">Cognitive Audit</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full text-[9px] font-label uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface-variant">Agent Extraction</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full text-[9px] font-label uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-surface-variant">Logic Mapping</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-80 h-80">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-primary/20 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-8 border border-secondary/20 rounded-full"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-7xl text-primary">psychology</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 02 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 pl-0 lg:pl-24 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(204,151,255,0.05)] relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1 h-full bg-secondary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-black text-outline-variant/10 absolute -top-4 -left-4">02</span>
                    <span class="font-label text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-6 block">Phase 02: Framework</span>
                    <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Structural Synthesis (Architect + Builder Agent)</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        Establishing the core architecture. The Architect defines the skeletal frame, and the Builder Agent rapidly generates the atomic component hierarchy and logic flow schematics.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-label text-on-surface">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">polyline</span> Agent-Generated Logic Flow
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-label text-on-surface">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">view_quilt</span> Atomic Hierarchies
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                <img alt="Blueprint schematic" class="w-full max-w-md grayscale opacity-40 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/20 shadow-2xl" data-alt="Technical blueprint of a user interface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDuEwREIdh0yssvRSZR_LdssJBc3_YvCq-k2-UtfCOsgk8Pwq2P5lz3wDnFgWBVaJSkONTtA0-xCYEkxv5emsyguTE0DoH5E_1dmQDly8PcABP2wDgzlB2x63eH7fSLjJjgEWlYvwrv75IHCtPCVXfC4DCLffA2ceP-bOy90qrw6M-7GTGhHBZxQdrciGsLXZDgHNpcpYyhMJ_WNskCDkzDvFGb2KMDyjRDWOtRXpeyk1Ec-ja_xNPYweUMJLFY7V8VmyiCOIcfb0ta"/>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 03 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 pr-0 lg:pr-24 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(204,151,255,0.05)] relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-primary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-black text-outline-variant/10 absolute -top-4 -right-4">03</span>
                    <span class="font-label text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-6 block">Phase 03: Aesthetic</span>
                    <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Aesthetic Refinement (Architect + UX Agent)</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        Application of the Synthetix Noir aesthetic. The UX Agent optimizes layouts for interaction fluidity while the Architect ensures the editorial typography and luminal accents match the brand's soul.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-lg">
                            <span class="text-primary font-headline text-xl block mb-1">Agent-Optimized</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-label text-on-surface-variant uppercase">Visual Latency</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-lg">
                            <span class="text-secondary font-headline text-xl block mb-1">Fluid</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-label text-on-surface-variant uppercase">Interaction Flow</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                <div class="w-full max-w-md aspect-square bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/20 overflow-hidden relative">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#262626]/40 backdrop-blur-xl opacity-40"></div>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl text-white/20 relative z-10">auto_awesome</span>
                    <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 flex gap-2 z-10">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-white/20"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 04 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 pl-0 lg:pl-24 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-12 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(204,151,255,0.05)] relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1 h-full bg-secondary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-8xl font-black text-outline-variant/10 absolute -top-4 -left-4">04</span>
                    <span class="font-label text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-6 block">Phase 04: Execution</span>
                    <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Autonomous Deployment (Architect + DevOps Agent)</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
                        The transition from design to production. Our specialized DevOps Agent manages the heavy-duty optimization and AWS deployment, ensuring clean code and 100% optimization.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-3">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-background bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-on-primary-container font-black">JS</div>
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-background bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-on-secondary-container font-black">TS</div>
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-background bg-surface-bright flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-on-surface font-black">TW</div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant">Agent Engine: 100%</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                <div class="p-8 border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-lowest">
                    <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant opacity-50">// INITIALIZING AGENT DEPLOYMENT</p>
                        <p>const swarm = new AgentSwarm();</p>
                        <p>swarm.deploy(architecture);</p>
                        <p>swarm.validate(&#123; mode: "autonomous" &#125;);</p>
                        <p class="text-primary mt-2">SWARM.STATUS = "ACTIVE";</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-48">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-16 md:p-24 text-center border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-primary/5 via-transparent to-secondary/5"></div>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 relative z-10 tracking-tight text-white">
                Ready to Initiate <br/> Your <span class="text-primary">Digital Evolution?</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 relative z-10 font-body text-lg">
                The protocol is ready. Let's map your brand's future architecture through a focused consultation.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center relative z-10">
                <button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dim text-on-primary-fixed px-12 py-5 rounded-md font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
                    Start a Consultation
                </button>
                <button class="border border-outline-variant/30 hover:bg-surface-container-highest px-12 py-5 text-white rounded-md font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black transition-all">
                    View Past Work
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
